These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different pets are kept: snake, frog
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, dubstep
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Pet   | snake  | frog |
| Music-Genre     | dubstep | r&b  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, brown
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, adventure
1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Color    | purple      | brown         |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, poker
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, purple
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Game   | poker | monopoly   |
| Color       | purple  | brown |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, techno
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, corn
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | techno |
| Food         | cucumber | corn    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
