.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-7::.
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | rabbit |
| Birthday      | april     | august  |

